Color Scheme:
  Toolbar text color: #ffffff
  Toolbars and buttons : #27AE60
  Remove button : #ff3b30


Font:
  Arial sans sarif


Others:
  1-Make Buttons rounded retangle.
  2-Use back icon from android studio assets to go back to pervious activity.
  3-Download the project "AORMS" from "Master" to make changes and upload in your "specified Branch".
  4-make every activity in "Landscape" .
  5-Use logo file (logo.png and Logo_with_transparent_background.png) as logo where needed.
  6-Make sure You have implemented all indents.


Rounded Rectangle button code (create a file rounded_button.xml and copy paste this code):
  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
  <shape xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" 
  android:shape="rectangle">
      <!-- redButton is #ff3b30 here. -->
      <solid android:color="@color/redButton" />
      <!-- buttonRadius is 18dp here. -->
      <corners android:bottomRightRadius="@dimen/buttonRadius"
          android:bottomLeftRadius="@dimen/buttonRadius"  
          android:topRightRadius="@dimen/buttonRadius"
          android:topLeftRadius="@dimen/buttonRadius"/>
  </shape>


Color redButton code(add this line in colors.xml):
  <color name="redButton">#893749</color>


Dimension buttonRadius(add this line in dimens.xml):
  <dimen name="buttonRadius">18dp</dimen>
